sequenceDiagram
    participant CP as Charge Point (OCTT)
    participant CS as Central System (SUT)

    Note over CP,CS: Test Case: TC_007_CSMS
    Note over CP,CS: Regular Start Charging Session – Cached Id

    Note over CP,CS: [EV driver plugs in the cable.]

    CP->>CS: 1. StatusNotification.req (connectorId=1, status=Preparing, errorCode=NoError)
    Note over CP: Validation: status must be Preparing
    CS-->>CP: 2. StatusNotification.conf

    Note over CP,CS: [EV driver presents identification (cached idTag).]

    CP->>CS: 3. StartTransaction.req (connectorId=1, idTag=<cached_id>, meterStart=0, timestamp=<current_timestamp>)
    CS-->>CP: 4. StartTransaction.conf (idTagInfo.status=Accepted, transactionId)
    Note over CP: Validation: idTagInfo.status must be Accepted

    CP->>CS: 5. StatusNotification.req (connectorId=1, status=Charging, errorCode=NoError)
    CS-->>CP: 6. StatusNotification.conf
    Note over CP: Validation: status must be Charging
